    "created_at": "2015-09-17T17:19:17Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-09-17T17:19:17Z",
    "body": "If you're running your app, by running `electron.exe path2App`, you are actually loading it through Electron's default_app, which has a menu, so that's why F11 works. If you instead package your app (either in the `resources\\app` directory or in the `resources\\app.asar` archive), the default menu won't exist so F11 won't toggle fullscreen.\n"
